-------------------H E L P    M E N U-------------------
----------------------------------------------------------

`League of legends Commands`

 **-opgg [sum name]** : gives you the oppgg

 **-champ [champ]** : info about the champion

 **-optop** : Gives you the meta toplaners in current patch 

 **-opjgl** : Gives you the meta junglers in current patch

 **-opmid** : Gives you the meta midlaners in current patch 

 **-opsup** : Gives you the meta supports in current patch 

 **-opadc** : Gives you the meta adcs in current patch


`Other Commands`

**-del [x]** : Delete x messages
**-kick @user** : kicks the user (admin only)
